Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.helperClasses.bezierCurves

Interface BijectiveMap<T,S>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of keys in the map
S - the type of values in the map
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractBijectiveMap, AbstractBijectiveMap.NumericBijectiveMap
public interface BijectiveMap<T,S>
A bijective map interface that allows for a one-to-one mapping between keys and values. This interface provides methods to put, get, invert, check existence, remove entries, and retrieve the forward and reverse maps.
